2\pi - \sin\left(\dfrac{5\pi}{12}\right)
\end{align*}
灯光交点C
Substituting $S_{radians}$ and $ \theta = \dfrac{5\pi}{12} $ into $S = \theta r$
\begin{align*}
10\pi = \dfrac{5\pi}{12} r
\end{align*}
灯光交点C
